Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.13,0:00:08.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(250,250)}普特利麥奧斯簡報室
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.01,0:00:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於Celestial Being在錫蘭島上的武力干預
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.94,0:00:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們失去了148名尊貴的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.16,0:00:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然Celestial Being主張根除紛爭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.24,0:00:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其行為只能說是擾亂國家秩序的恐怖活動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.64,0:00:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們人類革新聯盟要以堅決的態度來挑戰他們的恐怖行為
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.71,0:00:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被討厭了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.29,0:00:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.04,0:00:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  由於我們的所為  人革聯的軍備增強了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.16,0:00:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他們準備那麼做的話  那我們就只有繼續武力干預
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.82,0:00:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根除戰爭…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.87,0:00:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  只有這才是Celestial Being的本願
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:01:00.53,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外  為了不讓Celestial Being的暴行繼續下去  聯合…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.58,0:03:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地球化石燃料枯竭的公元2307年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.98,0:03:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用三個國家群所建造的三個軌道電梯和太陽光發電系統
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.40,0:03:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類甚至獲得了半永久性的能源供給
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  各國軍隊為了自己的威信和繁榮  而繼續著大範圍的戰爭遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  雖然已是24世紀  但人類依然沒有統一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.81,0:03:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對這樣的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.66,0:03:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推翻腐朽的人們出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.41,0:03:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有MS Gundam的私立武裝組織——Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.75,0:03:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們為了讓世界沒有紛爭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而展開了超越民族  國家  宗教的作戰行動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:04:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賦予Gundam Meister的新任務又要再次展開了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:11.50,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(250,250)}#04 對外交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.82,0:04:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖活動終於蔓延到市中心了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.22,0:04:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得在溫和派採取行動之前  推進改革…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.65,0:04:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.32,0:04:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了重振這個曾依賴於化石燃料的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.73,0:04:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有期待擁有太陽光發電系統的國家群的援助
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  我國並未參加軌道電梯的建設計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.96,0:04:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不具有能量供給權
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.52,0:04:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在致富之源的石油的輸出受限制的如今
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還會有國家肯無償地援助我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.45,0:04:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是為了尋求援助  議會才會恢復君主制度並推崇我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.91,0:05:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  要做的就只有一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此  情況可是愈發緊迫了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.75,0:05:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若國內繼續照這樣慌亂下去  那他們不久便會出現
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.03,0:05:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私立武裝組織——Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.76,0:05:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.80,0:05:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說過沒  阿里路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.58,0:05:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真IRA的活動停止聲明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.32,0:05:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那份聲明中雖然也有讚賞我們的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.76,0:05:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是臨時性的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只不過是害怕武力干預而先採取了行動罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若沒有我們  那他們會馬上重新開始活動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  根除紛爭並不是那麼簡單就能實現的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.88,0:05:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊  該休息時要好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.55,0:06:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就會忙起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.14,0:06:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實現長久的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.71,0:06:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此而存在的…Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.54,0:06:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何啊  中校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:16.65,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(250,250)}人革聯  總司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.24,0:06:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和Gundam交過手了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.95,0:06:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否毫無保留地告訴我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  就我個人的意見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個世界上並不存在能與那稱作Gundam的機體抗衡的MS
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那麼厲害的性能嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.27,0:06:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只不過是我的個人意見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.88,0:06:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話  叫你過來是對了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.93,0:06:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校  要把Gundam弄到手  先於聯合和AEU啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.23,0:06:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.56,0:06:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要新設立專門部隊  人員由你來挑選
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.76,0:06:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過有一個士兵得麻煩你照顧一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.58,0:06:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.23,0:06:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:06:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打攪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.20,0:07:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是超人機關技術研究所派來的超兵1號——蘇摩·佩麗絲少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超人機關？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.70,0:07:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令  難不成是那個計劃？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.30,0:07:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在水面下繼續著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.13,0:07:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高層將其視作對抗Gundam的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天於中校的專門部隊就職
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.12,0:07:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是也太年輕了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.34,0:07:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真的很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.11,0:07:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  不會吧  是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.72,0:08:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈·克洛斯羅德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.54,0:08:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沒錯  你還記得我的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  他是住隔壁的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.15,0:08:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.67,0:08:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那·F·清榮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.48,0:08:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背包和各部關節的強化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機體表面的耐射線塗層
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.80,0:08:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器選購的是Iris公司試製的新型來福槍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壯觀  教授
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  即使是啟動反重力系統
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.36,0:08:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在全速旋轉時也會受到12倍的重力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該說是正如所願
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.85,0:08:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  這就是中尉的Flag嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.69,0:09:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍華德·梅森準尉  達利爾·道奇上士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.74,0:09:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應格拉哈姆·艾卡中尉的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來對Gundam調查隊就職
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.37,0:09:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎  Flag Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪比特  白天的新聞看過沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.06,0:09:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有評論員說  把Celestial Being任命為世界警察如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.73,0:09:20.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(250,250)}聯合  總統宅邸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.24,0:09:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像聯合國  無需維持費用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大部分人都心中有鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.68,0:09:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國家亦然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.89,0:09:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能會有人和他們聯手的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.94,0:09:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總統  有報告稱塔利比亞將於明天發表聲明…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.26,0:09:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吠陀  告訴我你的預測…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.92,0:09:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我的預測一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.06,0:09:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應對計劃有12種
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.29,0:10:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論選哪一種  我們的立場都很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使知道是這樣  也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.26,0:10:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐  剛才塔利比亞發表了聲明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是塔利比亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.04,0:10:18.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯合雖然採用的是超過50的國家議會制
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.12,0:10:25.17,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其實是擁有太陽能分配權的美國一國的獨裁體制
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.73,0:10:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪比特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.84,0:10:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去舉行聯合的特別議會  並召集主要國家代表
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.56,0:10:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.25,0:10:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們塔利比亞共和國要脫離聯合  主張獨自的能源使用權
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.67,0:10:38.59,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(250,250)}人革聯  國家主席府邸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.47,0:10:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若本主張遭到反對  並受到他國的政治  軍事壓力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:44.97,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(250,250)}AEU中央議會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.48,0:10:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我國將以軍事力量進行對抗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我國堅決反對卑劣的美國支配
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.96,0:11:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔利比亞有動作了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.23,0:11:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然那個國家以前就有很強的反美意識
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.25,0:11:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但居然要脫離聯合  並單方面主張能源權利…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想為下一輪選舉做鋪墊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.57,0:11:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.42,0:11:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軌道電梯周圍國家形勢的惡化
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.29,0:11:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會給太陽光發電系統的運營造成障礙的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯合一定會接受美國的要求並下決心採取軍事干涉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.24,0:11:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而塔利比亞也一定預測到會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預測…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.20,0:11:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉  你知道塔利比亞為何會採取這樣的強行策略嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.32,0:11:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他們認為
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.67,0:11:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若聯合採取軍事行動  那Celestial Being會出來干預吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.30,0:11:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被引誘出來嗎  Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想說塔利比亞打算利用Celestial Being嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.49,0:11:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.96,0:12:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之所以能持以那種充滿恐嚇的強硬態度
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.54,0:12:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是因為塔利比亞位於軌道電梯附近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我國不同  有牌可使
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.55,0:12:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being真的會出現嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.65,0:12:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  說不定本國的未來\N會因Celestial Being如何應對塔利比亞而改變呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本國的命運…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是說可以利用他們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.36,0:12:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使知道是被利用  我們仍然會行動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.49,0:12:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  這才是Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.12,0:12:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務開始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.46,0:12:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯絡Gundam Meister他們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.47,0:12:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯合因議會中多數成員的贊成  而決定向塔利比亞派遣軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.09,0:12:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外  美國將獨自派兵…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.88,0:13:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔利比亞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.45,0:13:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.04,0:13:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解  瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.78,0:13:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios  阿里路亞·哈普提茲姆  進入干預行動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames  洛克恩·斯托拉托斯  出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.31,0:14:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia  刹那·F·清榮  出發
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.85,0:14:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於要和Gundam交手了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.12,0:14:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人期待  中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  這台特裝型Flag到底能和Gundam周旋多久…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  無論如何都有必要這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.78,0:14:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯合的艦隊和美軍第二艦隊抵達塔利比亞近海
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:39.17,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(250,0)}太平洋  塔利比亞近海
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.87,0:14:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴西的駐軍基地也調用了空中兵力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.03,0:14:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是要掌握塔利比亞主要城市的制空權
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.43,0:14:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那塔利比亞軍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.27,0:14:51.40,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(250,250)}塔利比亞軍  陸軍用MS部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.62,0:14:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在三個主要城市集結了陸軍用MS部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.71,0:14:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正可謂一觸即發呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.03,0:14:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐  要如何是好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.17,0:15:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早已定好了  我們要做的只有一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.66,0:15:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長  Gundam出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是Gundam嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.22,0:15:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是Blue Shark  目測確認了兩台Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.13,0:15:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正朝著首都方向去  請採取應對措施
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.87,0:15:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通訊被妨礙了  是Gundam做的好事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.91,0:15:35.04,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(250,0)}塔利比亞  首相府邸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.04,0:15:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首相  Celestial Being出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam散開了  估計分別是朝著三個主要城市去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.97,0:15:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想要武力干預嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以聯合和我們美軍為敵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.98,0:15:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若Celestial Being進行武力干預
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.09,0:15:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有助於塔利比亞的強硬態度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.59,0:16:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反過來  若不進行武力干預  而允許聯合的軍事行動的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.67,0:16:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他們的根除紛爭的行動理念就瓦解了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.60,0:16:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  要選哪一個呢  Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.40,0:16:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being會採取何種武力干預呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.31,0:16:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務開始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.36,0:16:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯合先採取了攻擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.13,0:16:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.20,0:16:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可什麼都還沒做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.09,0:16:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being的創始人——
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.59,0:16:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞·修亨伯格在聲明中已說過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.29,0:17:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being將放任戰爭的國家也作為武力干預的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.83,0:17:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確定塔利比亞為放任戰爭的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.96,0:17:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅逐目標
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.24,0:17:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios  開始干預行動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames  對目標進行狙擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.85,0:18:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然利用別人  太隨便了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.87,0:18:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  這是單方面的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.41,0:18:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam開始對塔利比亞軍展開攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.85,0:18:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam對我軍展開了攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.31,0:18:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱線聯絡布賴恩總統
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.86,0:18:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.57,0:18:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.49,0:18:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是將貴國視為引起紛爭的存在而展開攻擊的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.85,0:18:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對他們的行動表示遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.03,0:18:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  若能撤銷脫離聯合
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.39,0:18:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們很樂意為保護貴國而派遣軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.84,0:18:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.96,0:19:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我軍為了保護身為友好國家的塔利比亞共和國
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.47,0:19:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對Celestial Being展開攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.59,0:19:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美國的MS部隊出動了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.65,0:19:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和預料的一樣  推測是為防衛塔利比亞的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.57,0:19:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照任務  各Gundam開始撤退  向安全圈撤離
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真搞笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.45,0:19:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有機體接近Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.09,0:19:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是美軍的Flag
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美軍？  怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正以普通機兩倍以上的速度猛追Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.21,0:19:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台Flag是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.34,0:19:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就能和Gundam交手了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.57,0:19:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應對得不錯  總統
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.68,0:19:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.10,0:20:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.40,0:20:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得漂亮  中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.97,0:20:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.53,0:20:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特裝型Flag
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.72,0:20:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很想過過招
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  竟然還能在水中行動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.86,0:20:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泛用性太高了  Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.70,0:20:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會  居然攻擊塔利比亞軍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.91,0:20:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔利比亞還有美國好像都預測到會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.93,0:20:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預測到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.97,0:20:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到Celestial Being武力干預的塔利比亞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.52,0:20:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,率先借用了美軍的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.12,0:20:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來  塔利比亞國內的反美情緒便會消退
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.12,0:20:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從而可開展美國主導的政策
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.83,0:21:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔利比亞的現政權也因得到美國的援助而得以穩定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.62,0:21:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他國家也會避免重蹈塔利比亞的覆轍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.56,0:21:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會採用露骨的反美政策吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.06,0:21:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因這一系列的事件而受惠最多的是哪一方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.48,0:21:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若還不清楚的話  那你就沒有資格挽救本國
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.36,0:21:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿扎提斯坦王國第一公主——瑪麗娜·伊斯邁爾殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.97,0:21:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  是怎麼回事啊  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.17,0:21:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being攻擊了塔利比亞軍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.67,0:21:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個國家不是沒進行什麼戰爭或其它事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.62,0:21:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.05,0:21:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明說要讓人們放棄戰爭  卻又引起了戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.16,0:21:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.49,0:21:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界可沒那麼簡單哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.82,0:21:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界  並不簡單…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.20,0:00:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.96,0:23:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在低軌道平台的相遇  讓阿里路亞想起了過去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.09,0:23:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點吧  Kyrios  在生命消逝之前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.43,0:23:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  「脫離極限的領域」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.29,0:23:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法擺脫的重力束縛著Gundam


